The Gatekeepers of Science:  Some Factors Affectingthe Selection of Articles of Scientific Journals.ACrane, D.
  The norms of scientific behavior asdescribed by Merton include theprescription that scientific achievementsare to be judged without reference toscientists' social characteristics.  Thisarticle will attempt to assess the extentto which this norm is followed withrespect to the evaluation of articles byscientific journals.